{"tid":413314,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有關domain用唔用www問題","createTime":"2017-09-25T11:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T02:17:47.000Z","uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9ae3571fb82aa7e17318b075dbae1455c4fa57","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"我想強制用www，<a href=\"http://用301將domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%94%A8301%E5%B0%87domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=afedbba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">用301將domain.com</a>轉去<a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a>呢個方法其實啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一個問題，其實我啲網頁係放咗係www定public_html？好似係同一樣野？啲hosting係咪無論有無www都會入同一個file？"},{"pid":"b38547533d5a5282b61d6635f88102bb4a7b4e32","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想強制用www，<a href=\"http://用301將domain.com轉去www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%94%A8301%E5%B0%87domain.com%E8%BD%89%E5%8E%BBwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c1abf5fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">用301將domain.com轉去www.domain.com</a>呢個方法其實啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一個問題，其實我啲網頁係放咗係www定public_html？好似係同一樣野？啲hosting係咪無論有無www都會入同一個file？</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變咗做link"},{"pid":"e0589d2c124a76223ea94379d620935933562d60","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:16:45.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由鳩佢"},{"pid":"276b155c612e2eb2dfb5922b20f254e651fdf2a0","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"有關第二個問題，我個domain係成個name server指咗去hosting度的"},{"pid":"ef8d80b82036b2932a3e1ebf861e37b4b1f64fcf","tid":413314,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知自己做緊咩先...<br />\n如果你要用www, 咁你要整好subdomain 既 dns record 先喎..."},{"pid":"59ca5bc42c0e42fbb351a83e742ba8338744dd2b","tid":413314,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhost.com.hk%2Fhelp%2Fteach%2Fsubdomain.html&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c3f0875a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲hosting 好似會幫你做好哂..<br />\n至於你講果個301 redirect 去www 到.. 可以既.."},{"pid":"bc3c8542e35f500a9d523297538709d62546ef90","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你知唔知自己做緊咩先...<br />\n如果你要用www, 咁你要整好subdomain 既 dns record 先喎...</blockquote><br />\n係啊，個domain用緊hosting name server了<br />\n<br />\n之前我sub domain同main domain係分開做唔同嘢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://咁sub.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%92%81sub.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d0c97100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">咁sub.domain.com</a>就用cname，www又係用cname，咁裸域就301去www<br />\n<br />\n係家用nameserver反而唔識係個hosting度搞"},{"pid":"a2fbcb6f9c994e58e13432d9b7dd72e52676e49b","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhost.com.hk%2Fhelp%2Fteach%2Fsubdomain.html&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c3f0875a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲hosting 好似會幫你做好哂..<br />\n至於你講果個301 redirect 去www 到.. 可以既..</blockquote><br />\n咁即係唔正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？上網search咗九萬個方法non-www to www都係教我301<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c30ed524919ecbeddc7a97abbbd6b4792cb675","tid":413314,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both."},{"pid":"e42b852d8c3a615b0e850faa00042bed5b5aacdc","tid":413314,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhost.com.hk%2Fhelp%2Fteach%2Fsubdomain.html&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c3f0875a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mhost.com.hk/help/teach/subdomain.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲hosting 好似會幫你做好哂..<br />\n至於你講果個301 redirect 去www 到.. 可以既..</blockquote><br />\n咁即係唔正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？上網search咗九萬個方法non-www to www都係教我301<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法其實好正常, 只係我頭先唔知你一直host 緊, 奇怪啲人點解會知你有non-www 既link 姐.."},{"pid":"ba3243739e28d3b20a1b0b9b1391ef92171acfd6","tid":413314,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n仲有一個問題，其實我啲網頁係放咗係www定public_html？好似係同一樣野？啲hosting係咪無論有無www都會入同一個file？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mepopedia.com/forum/read.php?146,2304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmepopedia.com%2Fforum%2Fread.php%3F146%2C2304&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d1e8f9bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mepopedia.com/forum/read.php?146,2304</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔知有無理解錯.. 以我所知你想放邊都可以.. 只係config 上要你個sub-domain 指去邊個folder 姐.."},{"pid":"44194bc282d0d590b3d5286efead13bd20113d89","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n仲有一個問題，其實我啲網頁係放咗係www定public_html？好似係同一樣野？啲hosting係咪無論有無www都會入同一個file？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mepopedia.com/forum/read.php?146,2304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmepopedia.com%2Fforum%2Fread.php%3F146%2C2304&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d1e8f9bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mepopedia.com/forum/read.php?146,2304</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔知有無理解錯.. 以我所知你想放邊都可以.. 只係config 上要你個sub-domain 指去邊個folder 姐..</blockquote><br />\n唔係呢個，不過好小事，自己試完就知有無www都會指向同一個file，所以更加要301過去<br />\n<br />\n唔該兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a75860967d2412600a9fdf23c562037c0baecad","tid":413314,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"Recommendation 好似係 用 www<br />\n跟住 為 seo 應該做 URL rewrite or 301 redirect <br />\n喺 google analytics and search console set 個 preferred domain <br />\n<br />\nWww as Canonical URL:<br />\nMore scalable and allows cookieless domain <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.yes-www.org/why-use-www/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yes-www.org%2Fwhy-use-www%2F&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=21c54859\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yes-www.org/why-use-www/</a>"},{"pid":"5dc402a591707e58d325d4fabdd9ed1ef1a94ae5","tid":413314,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both.</blockquote><br />\n不嬲除咗 wildcard cert etc naked domain and www. Count as 2 domains <br />\n<br />\n非重要 site 用 let's encrypt 都已經夠 又免費又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhttp to https 都要做 301 redirect"},{"pid":"3c16353d905aa21d68222f5167add28b977828f8","tid":413314,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both.</blockquote><br />\n不嬲除咗 wildcard cert etc naked domain and www. Count as 2 domains <br />\n<br />\n非重要 site 用 let's encrypt 都已經夠 又免費又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhttp to https 都要做 301 redirect</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實係想打&ldquo;如果有https&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有見過無2個都買/gen, 7到hihi"},{"pid":"7eee0930e14d642a632c87f78102cafe7b82061e","tid":413314,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both.</blockquote><br />\n不嬲除咗 wildcard cert etc naked domain and www. Count as 2 domains <br />\n<br />\n非重要 site 用 let's encrypt 都已經夠 又免費又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhttp to https 都要做 301 redirect</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實係想打&ldquo;如果有https&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有見過無2個都買/gen, 7到hihi</blockquote><br />\n理論上 www. 同 naked domain 唔一定要指同一個 server. 一個 a record 一個 cname alias<br />\n所以會要兩張cert 不過大部分人都係揀定一個然後做 redirect <br />\n<br />\n不過係 convention 上多數係同一個<br />\n回應返 www 同 naked domain 係咪指同一個 folder"},{"pid":"2fe4f0bc46c44b0f22397853a886e9485a149336","tid":413314,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both.</blockquote><br />\n不嬲除咗 wildcard cert etc naked domain and www. Count as 2 domains <br />\n<br />\n非重要 site 用 let's encrypt 都已經夠 又免費又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhttp to https 都要做 301 redirect</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實係想打&ldquo;如果有https&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有見過無2個都買/gen, 7到hihi</blockquote><br />\n理論上 www. 同 naked domain 唔一定要指同一個 server. 一個 a record 一個 cname alias<br />\n所以會要兩張cert 不過大部分人都係揀定一個然後做 redirect <br />\n<br />\n不過係 convention 上多數係同一個<br />\n回應返 www 同 naked domain 係咪指同一個 folder</blockquote><br />\n我用緊namecheap，佢預設係同一個<br />\n<br />\nBTW仲有個問題，點解個hosting幫我個subdomain前面加www<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如我去set SSL嘅時候佢問我邊個domain，個subdomain前面有www"},{"pid":"27270708c209d41e0867b53f2742809650c9e41d","tid":413314,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用http 301 redirect all traffic from &quot;no www&quot; to &quot;www&quot; 無問題.<br />\n但係要留心如果https <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a> 同 <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.domain.com</a> 係2個name. generate cert要include both.</blockquote><br />\n不嬲除咗 wildcard cert etc naked domain and www. Count as 2 domains <br />\n<br />\n非重要 site 用 let's encrypt 都已經夠 又免費又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhttp to https 都要做 301 redirect</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實係想打&ldquo;如果有https&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有見過無2個都買/gen, 7到hihi</blockquote><br />\n理論上 www. 同 naked domain 唔一定要指同一個 server. 一個 a record 一個 cname alias<br />\n所以會要兩張cert 不過大部分人都係揀定一個然後做 redirect <br />\n<br />\n不過係 convention 上多數係同一個<br />\n回應返 www 同 naked domain 係咪指同一個 folder</blockquote><br />\n我用緊namecheap，佢預設係同一個<br />\n<br />\nBTW仲有個問題，點解個hosting幫我個subdomain前面加www<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如我去set SSL嘅時候佢問我邊個domain，個subdomain前面有www</blockquote><br />\n你睇個DNS 應該 a record 係 @ （naked domain) and www is a cname alias pointing to @ <br />\n<br />\nwww 本身都算係個 subdomain<br />\n<br />\n你有冇 screenshot 望？ 我都諗緊轉去 name cheap"},{"pid":"8eb176157d7ae6a45293e97d4137a3e876ee881f","tid":413314,"uid":3607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a351ba15fdb54698cbfb7618bdd9ebf0bbfcdfe4","tid":413314,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"簡單D睇你用咩server<br />\n<br />\n用IIS的話就用web.config寫個rewrite rules<br />\n類似咁<br />\n<br />\n&lt;rewrite&gt;<br />\n    &lt;rules&gt;<br />\n        &lt;rule name=&quot;Redirect to non-www&quot; stopProcessing=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br />\n            &lt;match url=&quot;(.*)&quot; negate=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/match&gt;<br />\n            &lt;action type=&quot;Redirect&quot; url=&quot;<a href=\"http://domain.com/{R:1}&quot;&gt;&lt;/action&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com%2F%7BR%3A1%7D%22%3E%3C%2Faction%3E&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a7e7bd7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com/{R:1}&quot;&gt;&lt;/action&gt;</a><br />\n            &lt;conditions&gt;<br />\n                &lt;add input=&quot;{HTTP_HOST}&quot; pattern=&quot;^domain\\.com$&quot; negate=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/add&gt;<br />\n            &lt;/conditions&gt;<br />\n        &lt;/rule&gt;<br />\n    &lt;/rules&gt;<br />\n&lt;/rewrite&gt;<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://ryanhayes.net/redirect-www-non-www-using-web-config/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fryanhayes.net%2Fredirect-www-non-www-using-web-config%2F&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=61c42fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ryanhayes.net/redirect-www-non-www-using-web-config/</a><br />\n<br />\n用Nginx的話就可以係conf file寫個rewrite url<br />\n<br />\nserver {<br />\n    server_name  <a href=\"http://www.domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.domain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0b130111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.domain.com</a>;<br />\n    rewrite ^(.*) <a href=\"http://domain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4fe5b1d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com</a>$1 permanent;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n只要你個domain既www有指去server就得<br />\n唔使搞DNS唔使搞name server<br />\nvery easy"}]}